<h2 id="what%20is%20kindeditor%3F">What is KindEditor?</h2>
<p>KindEditor is a lightweight, Open Source(LGPL), cross browser, web based WYSIWYG HTML editor. KindEditor has the ability to convert standard textareas to rich text editing.</p>
<h2 id="official%20site">Official site</h2>
<p><a href="http://kindeditor.org/">http://kindeditor.org/</a></p>
